1. *Svakoj* od njih je dao po jedan dolar. (He gave each of them one dollar.)
2. On je nastojao da pomogne *svakoj* osobi. (He was trying to help every person.)
3. On je odgovarao na *svakoj* primedbi. (He responded to every criticism.)
4. On je imao uticaj na *svakoj* političkoj stranci. (He had an influence on every political party.)
5. On je pomogao *svakoj* porodici. (He helped every family.)
6. On je ponudio svoju zaštitu *svakoj* osobi. (He offered his protection to every person.)